claim.claim-text:
1. A reflection type of earphone, comprising: 
a pair of wires with two ends, one of the ends connecting with a sound signal output of a connected device; 
a loudspeaker with an end, the end is connected to the other one of the ends of the wires, and providing a sound output; and 
a reflection disk, facing to the sound output, and having a plurality of bent strips to engage with the loudspeaker; 
whereby, the reflection disk is arranged to close to an acoustic meatus of an user such that the sound can be reflected by way of the reflection disk before entering the acoustic meatus to obtain a time postpone.
